import React from 'react'
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar'
import Products from '../components/Products'
import styled from 'styled-components'

const PageContainer = styled.div`
  width: 100vw;
  height: auto;
  background-color: #92a2af;
`

const FiltersContainer = styled.div`
  display: flex;
  
`
const SortContainer = styled.dev`
  display: flex;

`
const Text = styled.span`
  font-size: 2em;
`
const Selection = styled.select`
  
`
const Option = styled.option`
  
`

export default function ProductsList() {
  return (
    <PageContainer>
      DIOCANE
      <Navbar />
      <FiltersContainer>
        <SortContainer>
          <Text>Filter Products</Text>
          <Selection>
            <Option defaultSelected disabled>Color </Option>
            <Option>Blue</Option>
            <Option>Blue</Option>
            <Option>Blue</Option>
            <Option>Blue</Option>
          </Selection>
        </SortContainer>
      </FiltersContainer>
      <Products />
    </PageContainer>
  )
}
